          <title>
            <string language="en">Remembrance: Ann Chamberlain</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Erinnerung: Ann Chamberlain</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Souvenir : Ann Chamberlain</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Remembrance: Ann Chamberlain</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Remembrance: Ann Chamberlain</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ενθύμηση: ANN Chamberlain</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Remembrance: Ana Chamberlain</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Visual artist Ann Chamberlain transforms what are often intimidating public spaces into welcoming, inspirational, and creative environments. This Educator Guide discusses the history of public monuments and the Abraham Lincoln Brigade.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Humanities</string>
          </keyword>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sichtkünstler Ann Chamberlain wandelt um, was 
häufig allgemeine Platz in das Begrüßen, in inspirational und in 
kreative Umgebungen einschüchtern. Diese Erzieher-Anleitung 
behandelt die Geschichte der allgemeinen Denkmäler und der Abraham 
Lincoln Brigade.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">L'artiste visuel Ann Chamberlain transforme ce qui
intimident souvent les espaces publics dans l'accueil, inspiré, 
et les environnements créateurs. Ce guide d'éducateur discute 
l'histoire des monuments publics et de la brigade d'Abraham Lincoln.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O artista visual Ann Chamberlain transforma o que 
intimidating frequentemente espaços públicos em dar boas-vindas, em 
inspirational, e em ambientes creativos. Esta guia do educador 
discute o history de monumentos públicos e do brigade de Abraham 
Lincoln.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">L'artista visivo Ann Chamberlain trasforma che 
cosa stanno intimidendo spesso gli spazi pubblici dare il benvenuto, 
nel inspirational e negli ambienti creativi. Questa guida 
dell'educatore discute la storia dei monumenti pubblici e della 
brigata di Abraham Lincoln.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ο εικαστηκός καλλιτέχνης ANN Chamberlain 
μετασχηματίζει τι εκφοβίζει συχνά τους δημόσιους χώρους στα 
καλωσορίζοντας, εμπνευσμένα, και δημιουργικά περιβάλλοντα. 
Αυτός ο οδηγός εκπαιδευτικών συζητά την ιστορία των 
δημόσιων μνημείων και της ταξιαρχίας του Abraham Λίνκολν.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El artista visual Ana Chamberlain transforma qué 
están intimidando a menudo espacios públicos en dar la bienvenida, 
inspirational, y ambientes creativos. Esta guía del educador 
discute la historia de los monumentos públicos y de la brigada de 
Abraham Lincoln.</string>
          </description>
